<body>
	<p><b>Module Information</b></p>
	<p>This module is for oral health assessment. There are four parts to fill out for the examintaion of our partient: </p>
	<p>1.) Global information like patient name, date of birth, etc.</p>
	<p>2.) The oral mucosa, where you can record your observations and treatments for:</p>
	<ul type="square">
		<li>lips</li>
		<li>gum</li>
		<li>uvula</li>
		<li>soft palate</li>
		<li>hard palate</li>
		<li>tonsil</li>
		<li>tongue</li>
		<li>other notices</li>
	</ul>	
	<p>3.) Information like known disease, drugs, etc.</p>
	<p>4.) The dental status, where you have a shema for teeth and can record the status, treatment and psi for each tooth.</p>
	<br/>
	<p>You can create a new form, save, edit and print forms. Oral health is very important for preventive medical care, because this information can minimize the risk of other illness.</p>
